helperTargetAddress: The smart contract address this proposal will modify. Ethereum or ENS only.
helperFunctionName: The name of the function to be called if this proposal passes
helperFunctionSignature: The parameter types of the function (above) to be called
helperParameters: Parameters used to call the function (comma separated)
helperEthValue: Amount of ETH to send with the transaction (from your treasury)
stateModuleTip: This transaction was executed by a Safe{Wallet} module.
stateActiveTip: The proposal can be voted on. This is the initial state of all newly created proposals.
stateRejectedTip: The proposal failed due to another proposal being executed with the same nonce.
stateExecutableTip: The proposal is now able to be executed on chain.
stateFailedTip: The proposal failed to achieve quorum or did not get enough votes to pass.
stateClosedTip: The Snapshot proposal voting period is closed.
statePendingTip: The Snapshot proposal vote period has not begun yet.
stateTimelockedTip: The proposal has passed but cannot be executed until the timelock period has ended.
stateFreezeInitTip: The parent Safe has initiated a vote to potentially freeze this child Safe.
stateFrozenTip: The parent Safe has voted to freeze this child Safe.
stateTimelockableTip: The proposal can now be timelocked for execution.
stateExpiredTip: The proposal passed but was not executed within the designated execution period.
errorInvalidFragments: Invalid combination of function signature and parameters
votingPowerTooltip: This is your voting power at the time the snapshot was taken, which occurs at the moment of proposal creation.
proposalTitleHelper: A short title for this proposal
proposalDescriptionHelper: Add a brief description, markdown supported
proposalAdditionalResourcesHelper: A link to any discussion or formal documentation
transactionExecutionAlertMessage: Transactions execute in the order they are added
multisigMetadataMessage: This transaction contains the proposal's encoded metadata.

votingTooltip: Time remaining to cast your vote.
timeLockedTooltip: This proposal can be executed once its timelock period has passed.
executableTooltip: Time remaining to execute this proposal
